      "name": "Pump Pressure-Rise Curve Verification",
      "description": "CFD-predicted pump head versus flow rate curve compared against manufacturer-supplied hydraulic performance data. Agreement within 5% across the full operating range confirms adequate solver configuration prior to hemolysis validation.",
      "comparedAgainst": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/morrison-fda-pump-geometry-dataset",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/pressure-rise-cfd-run-2024-11"
