    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40-2018 standard. The primary validation result (VR-01) demonstrates mean absolute relative error of 4.3% against the 15% acceptance criterion, and correctly identifies the worst-case hemolysis operating condition. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
